Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

Update of the arcade classic hits the Dreamcast with far superior graphics and sound, to make this game a must own for all DC racing fans.

Customise your races, up to 39 CPU controlled cars on the 9 tracks (plus mirrored\reversed versions) over a
maximum of 40 laps and beat your rivals to unlock faster vehicles & improve your lap times.

Theres also the time trial & 2 player split screen mode to keep you coming back for more.

Get Ready For Your Rolling Start............